Former NFL running back Lawrence Phillips is suspected of killing his cellmate in a Central California prison .
Phillips , who was jailed in 2005 , is serving a sentence of more than 31 years for choking his girlfriend in San Diego and driving his car into three teens after a pickup football game in Los Angeles .
On Monday , prison officials revealed he is killing Damion Soward , a 37-year-old inmate from San Bernardino County serving 82 years to life for a first-degree murder conviction .